Description: Provides historical AIS data tracks via the exactEarth HVT API.

Title: MODIS (GeoTIFF-Bundle)
Description: Provides MODIS Full Scenes Nadir Bidirectional Reflectance Distribution Function (BRDF)-Adjusted Reflectance (NBAR) data in TIF format consisting of one file per band with metadata.

Description: Provides Sentinel-2 L2A MSI Full Scenes data in SAFE format.

Description: Imports DIMAP data from GCS or AWS into UP42 for processing.

Title: AIS - Query Vessel by ID
Description: Query Vessel by ID exactEarth Provides historical AIS data points for a vessel via the exactEarth HVP API.

Title: Import Data (GeoTIFF)
Description: Imports GeoTIFF data from GCS or AWS into UP42 for processing.

Title: Hexagon Aerial Imagery 15cm
Description: Provides RGB+NIR imagery with 15 cm GSD in GeoTIFF for urban areas and select wide areas in the US.

Title: Hexagon Aerial Imagery 30cm
Description: Provides RGB+NIR imagery with 30 cm GSD in GeoTIFF across the entire US, Europe and parts of Canada.

Title: Meteomatics - Weather/Ocean Data and Forecasts Map
Description: Provides historic, current, and forecast weather data globally.

Title: MODIS (GeoTIFF)
Description: MODIS optical data with daily revisit rate fetched using Global Imagery Browse Services (GIBS).

Title: NEXTMap 10 Elevation Data Suite
Description: Provides NEXTMap 10 DSM and DTM at 10 meter resolution.

Title: NEXTMap One Elevation Data Suite
Description: Provides NEXTMap One DSM and DTM at 1 meter resolution.

Title: NEXTMap 5 Elevation Data Suite
Description: Provides NEXTMap 5 DSM and DTM at 5 meter resolution.

Title: Airbus Basemap (Tile)
Description: Airbus Basemap layer in GeoTIFF format.

Title: OpenStreetMap Extraction
Description: Imports vector layers from OSM.

Title: Pléiades Display (Download)
Description: Pléiades imagery in its original DIMAP format. Pan-sharpened RGB and NIR (0.5 m) bands with 8 bits.

Title: Pléiades Display (Streaming)
Description: Pléiades imagery in GeoTIFF format. Pan-sharpened RGB and panchromatic (0.5 m) bands.

Title: Pléiades Primary
Description: Primary sensor image, not georeferenced or map-projected, and rigourous model metadata (attitude, ephemeris) allowing geometric processing (orthorectification – DEM extraction). RGB+NIR (2 m) and panchromatic (0.5 m) bands.

Title: Pléiades Reflectance (Download)
Description: Pléiades imagery in its original DIMAP format. RGB, NIR (2 m) and panchromatic (0.5 m) bands with 12 bits.

Title: Landsat-8 Level 1 (GeoTIFF)
Description: Provides Landsat-8 imagery in GeoTIFF format.

Title: Sentinel-2 Level 2 (GeoTIFF)
Description: Provides Sentinel-2 imagery in GeoTIFF format.

Title: Sentinel-1 L1 GRD (GeoTIFF)
Description: Provides Sentinel-1 L1 GRD Full Scenes data in GeoTIFF format.

Title: Sentinel-1 L1 GRD (SAFE)
Description: Provides Sentinel-1 L1 GRD Full Scenes data in SAFE format.

Title: Sentinel-1 L1 SLC (SAFE)
Description: Provides Sentinel-1 L1 SLC Full Scenes data in SAFE format.

Title: Sentinel-2 L1C (GeoTIFF)
Description: Provides Sentinel-2 L2A clipped data in GeoTIFF format.

Title: Sentinel-2 L1C (SAFE)
Description: Provides Sentinel-2 L1C MSI Full Scenes data in SAFE format.

Title: Sentinel-3 (NetCDF)
Description: Provides Sentinel-3 Full Scenes data in NetCDF format.

Title: Sentinel-5P (NetCDF)
Description: Provides Sentinel-5P Full Scenes data in NetCDF format.

Title: SPOT 6/7 Display (Download)
Description: SPOT imagery in its original DIMAP format. Pan-sharpened RGB and NIR (1.5 m) bands with 8 bits.

Title: SPOT 6/7 Display (Streaming)
Description: SPOT imagery in GeoTIFF format. RGB and panchromatic (1.5 m) bands.

Title: SPOT 6/7 Reflectance (Download)
Description: SPOT imagery in its original DIMAP format. RGB, NIR (6 m) and panchromatic (1.5 m) bands with 12 bits.

Title: Import Data (GeoJSON)
Description: Imports GeoJSON vector data from GCS or AWS into UP42 for processing.

Title: Weather/Ocean data and forecasts
Description: Provides historic, current, and forecast weather data globally.

Description: Provides Sentinel-2 L2A clipped data in GeoTIFF format.

Description: Provides Sentinel-5P level-3 dataset for given time range and AOI.

Title: OneAtlas WorldDEM Full Resolution
Description: Provides a worldwide, consistent, and high precision Digital Surface Model (DSM) at 12 m resolution in GeoTIFF format.

Description: Provides historic, current, and forecast weather data globally.

Title: Weather Data for Energy and Power
Description: Provides historic, current, and forecast weather data globally.

Description: Provides historic, current, and forecast weather data globally.

Title: ESA Sentinel-2 L2A Analytic (GeoTIFF)
Description: Provides Sentinel-2 L2A clipped data in GeoTIFF format.

Title: MODIS
Description: A simple (and free) data block providing MODIS optical data with daily revisit rate fetched using Global Imagery Browse Services (GIBS). This is a starting point for anybody who intends to implement a data block.

Title: K-Means Clustering
Description: A simple processing block applying k-means clustering to an image. Can be used as an example for using more traditional machine learning algorithms.

Title: Sentinel-2 Super-resolution
Description: Super-resolves all bands of an Sentinel-2 image to 10m. This is a starting point for anybody who intends to implement a processing block using deep learning and GPUs.

Title: Sharpening
Description: A basic processing block implementing a high-pass sharpening filter. This is a starting point for anybody who intends to implement a processing block.

Title: SNAP Polarimetric Processing
Description: Converts Sentinel-1 GRD (radar) data into a GeoTIFF by using SNAP.
